data.name: _Label28_6.Text
data.value: Enter in the band plan as given. If there is only one frequency available, enter it in the Lower Frequency column in addition to Spacing and Offset. Once ALL information is in, click on 'Auto Upper' to calculate the upper frequency automatically.

data.name: chkTrnPriScan.ToolTip
data.value: Trunked channels can be assigned priority. When the scanner is monitoring the control channel, channels you tag as priority are given a higher priority over non-priority channels when they become active.
